<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />For in the day of trouble he will hide me in his shelter;</para>

<para style="q1">in the cover of his tent he will conceal me.</para>

<para style="q1">He will lift me high on a rock!</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />Then my head will be lifted up above my enemies all around me,</para>

<para style="q1">and I will offer sacrifices of joy in his tent!</para>

<para style="q1">I will sing and make songs to Yahweh!</para>

